    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Create a circle: deploy + initialize + (optionally) the creator's join &\\ndeposit \\xe2\\x80\\x94 ALL atomic in the deploy transaction. Runs once, at deploy.\\n\\nIf `creator_deposit > 0` the creator becomes member #1 with their deposit\\nlocked in the SAME transaction; if that transfer fails (e.g. insufficient\\nbalance) the constructor traps and the whole deploy reverts \\xe2\\x80\\x94 no half-built\\ncircle, no orphaned funds. Pass `creator_deposit == 0` for a pure-organizer\\ncircle (the creator funds later, or never participates).\\n\\nAuth: only `creator` signs \\xe2\\x80\\x94 they authorize creating their own circle and\\nmoving their own deposit. `admin` is stored for protocol upgrades only; it\\ndoes NOT gate creation, start(), or dissolve() (those are the creator's\\nauthority \\xe2\\x80\\x94 there is no system-admin power over a circle's lifecycle).",
      "name": "__constructor",
      "inputs": [
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "admin",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "creator",
          "type_": "address"
        },
